---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn more about Riven and our mission to provide valuable insights and resources.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          About Us
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We're on a mission to share knowledge and insights that help you grow.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose mx-auto">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          Riven was founded with a simple belief: knowledge should be accessible to everyone. 
          We bring together experts from technology, design, and business to create content 
          that inspires and educates.
        </p>
        
        <h2>What We Cover</h2>
        <p>
          Our blog covers a wide range of topics including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Technology</strong> - Latest trends in software development, AI, and emerging tech</li>
          <li><strong>Design</strong> - UI/UX best practices, design systems, and creative inspiration</li>
          <li><strong>Research</strong> - Data-driven insights and industry analysis</li>
          <li><strong>Management</strong> - Leadership, team building, and productivity tips</li>
          <li><strong>Customer Success</strong> - Building better customer experiences</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <p>
          We're a diverse team of writers, developers, and designers passionate about 
          creating high-quality content. Our contributors bring years of industry 
          experience and fresh perspectives to every article.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          Have questions or want to collaborate? We'd love to hear from you. 
          <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> and let's start a conversation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
